product_title: Pulox - Juego de vasos para ventosaterapia (2 unidades, tamaño grande), color rosa
product_description:
-
Copas de masaje para un masaje de ventosas profesional.

Las ventosas son un tratamiento tradicional, que se ha aplicado desde la antigüedad. Al aspirar la piel se produce un vacío en el vaso que a su vez crea una presión que estimula los puntos de acupuntura de la superficie del cuerpo. Un masaje de ventosa puede ayudar a estimular la circulación sanguínea y el metabolismo, dispersar una retención sanguínea, prevenir la celulitis, así como estirar el tejido conjuntivo. Los vasos están fabricados en cristal, por lo que se pueden limpiar y desinfectar fácilmente.

- Vasos para ventosaterapia con bolas de succión.
- Para ventosaterapia profesional y sin fuego.
- Bordes amplios y reforzados.
- Gran capacidad de absorción.
- Bajo peso.
- Fáciles de usar.
- Se deslizan fácilmente sobre la piel.
- Material: cristal.
Consejo para el masaje de ventosas:
- Antes del masaje, ponte algo de aceite corporal o aceite para masajes sobre la zona que se vaya a masajear o succionar. Así resulta más fácil y cómodo deslizar las ventosas sobre la piel. Muchos aceites tienen un efecto calor que vuelve el masaje de ventosas muy agradable y propaga una sensación de bienestar por todo el cuerpo.
- Mueve las ventosas sobre la piel, agarrando el cristal desde arriba con cuidado y suavidad. Gracias al aceite puedes retirar las ventosas con facilidad y moverlas sobre la piel sin mucho esfuerzo. No ejerzas demasiada presión sobre los vasos, ya que de lo contrario podrían romperse. No tires de la bola de succión, ya que podría perderse la presión o soltarse del cristal.
- Cuidado con el cristal: El cristal siempre es frágil. Por favor, no tires los vasos, no dejes que se caigan y no los arrojes contra otros objetos o paredes.
product_bullet_point:
Ventosa de vidrio con bola de succión extraíble.
Para ventosaterapia profesional sin fuego y masajes de ventosas.
De cristal auténtico. Tamaños: 52 mm, 62 mm. Color de la bola de succión: azul, marrón, verde o rosa.
Consejo: pon algo de aceite corporal o aceite para masajes sobre la piel antes del masaje de ventosas y mueve las ventosas sobre la piel, agarrando el cristal desde arriba con cuidado y suavidad.
Los vasos para ventosaterapia se deslizan mejor sobre el aceite, el masaje es muy agradable y propaga una sensación de bienestar por todo el cuerpo.

product_title: Your First 365 Days in Real Estate: How to Build a Successful Real Estate Business: Starting with Nothing
product_description:
The audiobook Your First 365 Days in Real Estate was nominated for a SOVAS in 2019 in the category of “Best Audiobook Narration - Business or Education”.

Your successful career in real estate starts here!

The first 365 days of working in real estate can be one of the most tumultuous times in your career - full of hard lessons, heart breaks, and hard work. Just because you have a license, doesn’t mean you have a business.

But if you get the important stuff right, a great future is yours for the taking.

This honest, eye-opening, and completely practical insider's guide shows you how to get where you want to be - even if you're starting from nothing.

Author and successful real estate agent Shelley Zavitz reveals in unprecedented detail:

  • What to expect the first year of your career
  • How to implement systems that will impact your business in the next 90 days
  • How to build a marketing plan in a digital world
  • How to work your contacts to start your referral pipeline
  • How mindset can make or break your business and what to do about it
  • Why surrounding yourself with the right people is essential

Shelley shares her own story as a new real estate agent - including how she built a brand starting with a network of just four people in a totally new city.

The book also comes complete with worksheets, hot lists, and examples of great branding so that you can catapult your business into the fast lane right now.

Your First 365 Days in Real Estate is the number one resource for new agents in the industry - don't miss out on your potential as a realtor without it.

product_title: Bottleneck Breakthrough: How to Find & Fix Your #1 Business Challenge to Unlock Sustainable Growth, Fast
product_description:
You can apply the Bottleneck Breakthrough Method to the predictable growth plateaus in every business, and at every stage of revenue, whether you're at $100k or $100M.

Every day a new silver bullet comes out promising to grow your business, increase your profit margins, and make your life as a business owner easier. Unfortunately, most of them don't work, wasting your time and money. Plus, they take your attention away from other more worthwhile opportunities. The ones that do work for others just never seem to work for you. Blanket prescriptions are like that, never quite hitting the mark for all but the few with the exact symptoms.

Instead of a blanket prescription that will generally help every business at every stage of growth, the more effective approach is to find a specific solution that hits the bull's eye for your unique situation. This creates the greatest improvement possible with the least amount of effort and risk.

That's the Bottleneck Breakthrough Method.

You can apply it to the predictable growth plateaus in every business, and at every stage of revenue, whether you're at $100K or $100M. Best of all, it builds on what you already do well, so you don't have to overhaul your entire business to get results.

The goal of this book is to become a reliable and powerful tool for you to grow your business, as it already has for many others.

product_title: Spill Proof Tumbler Lid with Angled Stainless Steel Straw + Silicone Straw Tip + Straw Cleaning Brush for Yeti Rambler or Ozark Trail Tumblers (30oz, Black)
product_description:
Replacement Leak-Proof Combination Straw and Sipping Lid for 20oz and 30oz Yeti Rambler and Ozark Trail Tumblers

Whether you want to slowly sip a hot drink, chug a cold one or turn your tumbler into a sippy cup.

Take your favorite tumbler on the go and have peace of mind. This lid accessory kit replaces the standard, leaky lid that came with your Yeti Rambler or Ozark Trail tumbler. Our lid sits firmly in place so it will not accidentally pop off should your tumbler actually take a "tumble".

The included 18/8 stainless steel straw has a large 7mm inside diameter to keep up with your thirst. When inserted in the center opening, the straw will not loosely slide out and leakage will be minimal.

All high quality materials are BPA-free and safe. Our exclusive offering includes a comfortable silicone tipped stainless steel straw. This insulated straw tip reduces the chill factor if you have sensitive teeth or gums and protects from inadvertent jabbing.

Tips for Use and Care

To ensure a full and proper seal during transport, push the tab down all the way until it is flush against the lid.

When opening, press down on tab to engage lock notch to prevent it from hitting your nose tip while drinking.

When refilling tumbler with straw already inserted, keep tab open to vent or remove straw before pressing down on lid. If tab is closed, fluid may squirt out of straw due to vacuum seal.

The lid will no longer be leak-proof when the straw is inserted into center vent plug hole but splashing will be minimal. The straw can be inserted in either opening on the 30oz size lids but the center hole offers the most splash control.

All items are top rack dishwasher safe. We advise washing immediately after smoothies and shakes to avoid encrustment.

Contact Us

If there are any product issues, please contact Thermalyfe for support.
product_bullet_point:
Fits 20oz or 30oz YETI Rambler and OZARK Trail TUMBLERS - Have peace of mind when you are on the move with our spill and splash proof lid. Replace the standard lid on your Yeti or Ozark so you have a 3-in-1 option to seal, sip, chug or suction through a straw.
No More Leaks Splashes or Spills - Our unique tumbler lid maintains an airtight seal when you are on the go so no more accidental splashes and spills on your favorite shirt or auto interior.
Combination Straw or Sipping - Get the best of both worlds in this combination package set! For hot drinks, open up the flap for slow slipping. For chilled drinks, use the perfectly sized straw for easy suction.
Comfort Straw Tip - Includes a soft silicone straw tip sleeve to protect your teeth and gums. Prevents jabbing yourself with the straw and insulates your lips from the cold or heat transfer.
Easy Cleaning - Includes a sturdy straw brush to let you scrub clean the inside of the straw. All items are top rack dishwasher safe.

»Einfach brillant. In einer Zeit, in der die Sexualität von Frauen zu den am hitzigsten diskutierten Themen gehört, führt kein Weg an diesem Buch vorbei.« Vogue

»Aufwühlend … Die Geschichten von Taddeos Protagonistinnen – Sloane, Lina und Maggie – handeln allesamt vom Verbotenen: Dreiecksbeziehungen, Dominanz und Unterordnung, Sex mit Minderjährigen. »Ich weiß nicht, wann mich ein Buch zuletzt so tief berührt hat wie Three Women – Drei Frauen. product_title: Surviving Parental Alienation: A Journey of Hope and Healing
product_description:
Half of all marriages end, and, when they do, most parents hope to achieve a "good divorce" in which they can amicably raise their children with their former spouse. Unfortunately, about 20% of divorces are high-conflict, involving frequent visits to court, allegations of abuse, and chronic disagreements regarding parenting schedules. 

In response to this conflict, some children become aligned with one parent against the other - even a parent who has done nothing to warrant the hostile rejection of their formerly loving children. These "targeted" parents suffer from the loss of time with their children, the pain of watching their children become distant, even cruel, and the uncertainty of not knowing if and when their children will come back to them. These parents are on a painful journey with an uncertain outcome. Surviving Parental Alienation fills the tremendous need for concrete help for these parents. 

Too often parental alienation stories that are shared by word of mouth, on the internet, or in books depict unending pain and frightening outcomes. Surviving Parental Alienation provides true stories and information about parents who have reconnected with their lost and stolen children, and offers better insight and understanding into what exactly parental alienation is and how to handle it.

product_description:

“Hold on tight. . . . This novel will give you whiplash as you rabidly turn pages. . . . May be [Lee Child’s] best.”—USA Today
 
New York City. Two in the morning. A subway car heading uptown. Jack Reacher, plus five other passengers. Four are okay. The fifth isn’t. And if you think Reacher isn’t going to get involved . . . then you don’t know Jack.
 
Susan Mark, the fifth passenger, had a big secret, and her plain little life was being watched in Washington, and California, and Afghanistan—by dozens of people with one thing in common: They’re all lying to Reacher. A little. A lot. Or just enough to get him killed. A race has begun through the streets of Manhattan, a maze crowded with violent, skilled soldiers on all sides of a shadow war. For Jack Reacher, a man who trusts no one and likes it that way, the finish line comes when you finally get face-to-face and look your worst enemy in the eye.

Instrucciones de depiladora con luz pulsada:
1: La depiladora de luz pulsada hará que el efecto sobre la raíz del cabello sea más eficaz, antes de usarla, debes afeitar el vello y secar la piel. Utiliza una toallita de alcohol médico para limpiar la ventana del flash.

5: Coloque la ventana flash vertical y firmemente sobre su piel donde quiera retirarla. Solo unos segundos a partir del momento en que esté en contacto con la piel.

¿A qué frecuencia debo utilizar esta depilación?
Un ciclo de depilación utiliza de 6 a 12 veces.
1. Utilizando una vez por semana las primeras 4 semanas.
2. Utilizar una vez cada 2 semanas después de 4 semanas.
3. Si encuentras que hay nuevo vello después de 6 – 12 tratamientos, puedes renovar el tratamiento una vez cada 2 – 4 semanas para un resultado óptimo.
4. El resultado varía de una persona a otra, utilízalo con menos frecuencia cuando la zona del pelo crezca una pequeña cantidad.

4 semanas: el 75 % de los folículos del pelo comienzan a atrofiarse, el crecimiento del vello ralentiza y se adelgaza.
8 semanas: el 85 % del pelo ha sido inhibido el crecimiento, el vello se reduce significativamente.
12 semanas: el 95 % de la superficie ha sido completado la depilación y lograr el objetivo de inhibir el crecimiento de forma sostenible.

1 x IPL depilación luminosa (depiladora con luz pulsada).

Uso profesional:
Paso 1: limpie las uñas, luego corte la superficie de las uñas en un proceso de manicura normal.
Paso 2: Agite bien el barniz, puede equilibrar el color del barniz. (Importante)
Paso 3: Aplique el barniz de gel de color, luego polimerice con el secador de uñas. Aplicar la capa 2 si es necesario. Curar con el secador de uñas después de cada capa durante 30 a 60 segundos.
Paso 4: Cúbralo con la capa superior, luego séquelo con un secador de uñas durante 30 a 60 segundos. Paso 5: Retire la superficie pegajosa con algodón empapado en el limpiador. Paso 6: ¡Disfruta de tu manicura de 14 días!

Cómo eliminar:
Paso 1: Remoje el algodón en acetona.
Paso 2: Envuelva cada clavo con papel de aluminio y deje aprox. 10 minutos, compruebe si está listo, de lo contrario deje unos minutos más.
Paso 3: utilice un bastoncillo o un empujador de color naranja para cortar las cutículas para eliminar el gel ablandado

product_description:
Color: White and gray Pull and Stick Wallpaper

Material: Vinyl Self Adhesive Wallpaper

Roll Size: 17.7" wide x 236.2" long, covers 29 sq.ft 

Usage: Wall decoration, glass, vinyl, Kitchen counter, furniture, crafts, bookcases, cabinets and drawers, counter tops, closet shelving, Shelf, pantry areas etc.


Instruction For Use:

1. It can be placed on any smooth clean and dry surface like shelf, board, wood cabinet,drawer,walls,window,glass etc. It is best applied at room temperature.

2. Sand down rough surfaces prior to sticking. Clean large surfaces with mild soap and water.

3. Measure the surface to cover. Cut the film into right size, leaving about 5cm extra overlap on all edges is beter.

4. Peel off the backing paper evenly with one hand whilst smoothing the film to the surface. With your other hand, from the center to edges. For this it's better to use a soft cloth.

5. Creases and air bubbles can be removed by applying light pressure from the center to the edges. Pierce stubborn bubbles with a needle and squeeze the air out. 


Notes: 

1. Color tones can vary due to lighting in the room, pictures on wall for reference only. 

2. Please buy enough rolls at a time to make sure they come from the same batch to avoid color difference.

product_title: UNISHOP Set 6 Láminas de Azulejos Adhesivos para Pared, Efecto 3D e Impermeables, Vinilo Decorativo con Pegatina para Cocina y Baño
product_description:
Cómo instalar:

1. Limpiar bien la pared para quitar todo el polvo y manchas (si la superficie no es lisa o está sucia o aceitosa, es posible que el adhesivo no se pegue bien).

2. Espere hasta que la pared esté totalmente seca.

3. Medir la pared y dibujar marcas con un nivel para crear al menos una línea de referencia vertical y una horizontal para guiar la colocación de las baldosas.

4. Despegue el papel de la parte posterior de la pegatina y luego péguelo en la pared.

5. Alinee con cuidado las siguientes baldosas adhesivas para que coincidan con las anteriores correctamente.

6. Nuestras baldosas se pueden recortar con tijeras para adaptar su forma a los interruptores, enchufes y a la pared en general.

Inoxidable y desmontable.

Tamaño:

Estante (Ordinario): 11.8 x 4.3 x 3.5 pulgadas (30 x 11 x 9 cm)
Estante (Grande): 12.2 x 4.7 x 1.4 pulgadas (31 x 12 x 9 cm)

La caja contiene:
2 x Recipiente de ducha
3 x Adhesivos
1 x Manual

Guía de Instalación:
1, Limpie la superficie donde se vaya a instalar.
2, Retire la envoltura trasera, y después aplique el adhesivo sobre la superficie limpia.
3, Cuelgue la cesta para la ducha en los ganchos.

Para un uso óptimo:
1, Utilizar el producto pasadas 24 horas desde su instalación.
2, Si necesita quitar la envoltura del adhesivo trasero, recomendamos usar un secador de pelo para calentar el adhesivo y después retirarlo.
3, Solo pegue el adhesivo en superficies lisas y duras. Por favor, no pegar el adhesivo sobre paredes pintadas o papel de empapelar pared ya que quitará la pintura o el papel de empapelar la pared.
4, Tenga en cuenta que el adhesivo NO es reutilizable. Si necesita mover el lugar de instalación, puede comprar más adhesivo aquí: https://www.amazon.es/dp/B07DBW9JQK.
product_bullet_point:
2 Piezas: Gran variedad de usos para cumplir con tus demandas. Proporciona un lugar conveniente para guardar botellas de champú, acondicionador y gel de baño. Ideal para cuartos de baño, baños de incitado, tocadores, etc.
Libre de Daños: Simplemente retire la protección y úselo sin necesidad de taladrar paredes, no requiere uso de herramientas adicionales. El nanoadhesivo funciona mejor en baldosas de cerámica, vidrio, granito, acero inoxidable y cualquier superficie lisa y dura.
Diseño Desmontable: El estante puede ser reciclado y reusado tras separarlo de los ganchos adhesivos. Tenga en cuenta que el adhesivo NO es reutilizable.

product_title: Red & Blue Litmus Paper Acid/Base pH Indicator Strips Combo Pack with 200 Strips | Qualitative No Color Chart Tests
product_description:
Students can test solutions for acid or base determination. Easy-to-use red litmus paper turns blue for bases and blue litmus turns red for acids. 100 strips of each. Not for measuring the pH of natural waters, such as streams, rivers and lakes.

Instructions:
Remove one litmus test paper from the vial, being careful not to touch the strip anywhere other than where you grasp it.
Dip the strip into the solution to be tested for 1-2 seconds and remove.
The red test strip will turn blue in seconds if dipped into a solution that is a base, and will remain unchanged if not. The blue test strip will turn red in seconds if dipped into a solution that is a base, and will remain unchanged if not.
product_bullet_point:
Comes with 2 portable vials, each filled with easy to use, pre-cut strips
No external reagents or chemicals needed for accurate testing of solutions
A simple way to determine without a doubt if a solution is acidic or basic, with a second test to confirm your findings
No color chart needed to determine findings; these tests are designed for determining if the pH is above or below a certain level NOT giving a precise pH value

product_title: Beyond Sanctuary (Sacred Band Series Book 2)
product_description:
THE SACRED BAND GOES NORTH – TO WAR!
Here is the new, revised and expanded Author’s Cut edition of BEYOND SANCTUARY, the first ever full-length novel to take you BEYOND the notorious Thieves World™ fantasy universe, where gods still stalk the land, warring with demons and human sorcerers and trampling unfortunate humanity underfoot.
If you like stories of bold brave knights employed in meritorious duty, or tales of ladies delicate and fair, be warned. Beyond Sanctuary, set at the foot of notorious Wizardwall, may be too much for your sensibilities. There wizards, bards, and maidens mingle with murderers and thieves, and the fight breaking out at the next table may be the one that ends your life.
The hero of BEYOND SANCTUARY is Tempus, leader of mercenaries and warrior-servant of Vashanka, god of storm and war. With Niko, Cime, and the Froth Daughter Jihan, Tempus faces the archmage Datan and his unholy followers – in a battle for the Rankan Empire’s survival and that of his very soul. BEYOND SANCTUARY is the first novel in Janet Morris’ BEYOND series, followed by BEYOND THE VEIL and BEYOND WIZARDWALL.

About the Author:
Janet Morris is a bestselling novelist who is also well-known as the creator of the Sacred Band of Stepsons series and member of the THIEVES’ WORLD™ writing team. Her Sacred Band of Stepsons books include her BEYOND TRILOGY (BEYOND SANCTUARY, BEYOND THE VEIL, BEYOND WIZARDWALL), TEMPUS, and, with Chris Morris, THE SACRED BAND, THE FISH THE FIGHTERS AND THE SONG-GIRL, CITY AT THE EDGE OF TIME, TEMPUS UNBOUND, and STORM SEED.

Snapshot guides are a great choice for travelers visiting a specific city or region, rather than multiple European destinations. They include good-value hotel and restaurant recommendations, with no introductory information (such as overall trip planning, when to go, and travel practicalities).

How to install:

Remove dirt from the windshield and bracket suction cups before installing the bracket. 1. Install the suction cup on the camera.

3. Press the suction cup firmly against the windshield and push the bracket down firmly
4. Plug the USB car charger into the cigarette lighter socket of the car.
6. Wiring the USB cable along the car’s gaps.
7. Place the end of the USB cable a few turns on the rear view mirror to prevent the recorder from falling.
8. Plug the Micro USB head of the car charger into the camera's USB port
9. Adjust the camera to an appropriate angle to ensure that the front of the car is visible from the camera screen.

Connect the rear camera's Terminal (2.5 mm diameter) directly to the AV IN port of the camera.

▪Please format SD Card (Not Included, Class 10, 32GB max SDHC card) on your dash cam before using; SD card is not included, please purchase a memory card separately.

▪It require a name band Class10 or higher micro SD card,Format your SD card on the camera first before using.

▪Record Do not remove the TF card during the recording process.

▪For cleaning, wipe gently with a soft cloth. Do not use any chemicals for cleaning. ▪In case of overheating, unwanted smoke or unpleasant smell from the device, unplug it immediately from the power outlet to prevent hazardous fire.

product_title: Blender Rubber Coupler, AP2930430, PS401661, 9704230, SA9704230
product_description: Brand new rubber blender coupler, 9704230. This is a non-oem coupler. The blender's rubber coupling is designed to break if the blender is under strain. This will often happen if the food being chopped is too hard or being chopped at too higher speed. The part failing prevents the motor from more severe damage.The coupler/clutch has six rubber teeth which grip the underside of the blade in the blending jug. The clutch is secured to the blender spindle (which is made of steel) with a reverse aluminum thread. i.e. you turn clockwise to undo it which is the opposite to normal.There are two ways to remove the old clutch. First you can use a thin 7mm spanner to grip the flats on the spindle under the coupler then turn the coupler clockwise. Second you can use a large flat bladed screwdriver to gently pry the coupler off the spindle. If you use the second method the aluminium thread in the coupler will be stripped as aluminum is softer. This is not a problem as the coupler will need replacing anyway. Make sure you clean off any pieces of aluminum left in the thread on the spindle.
product_bullet_point:
Replaces part numbers: AP2930430, 831718, AH401661, EA401661, PS401661
This is a non-OEM part.

product_description: Best Plantar Fasciitis Night SplintThis plantar night splint is a favorite both because it works and for its comfortable fit. Another reason many consider this to be the best night splint for plantar fasciitis and Achilles tendonitis is its highly affordable price that does not in any way translate to lesser quality. (See other plantar fasciitis night splints.)This plantar fasciitis night splint holds the foot in a mild dorsiflexion, which stretches the plantar fascia while one sleeps. Keeping the foot in this position can also help when it comes to Achilles tendonitis treatment as this also provides a light stretch of the Achilles tendon and calf, preventing the tendon from tightening up. An added benefit is that it can also help with the tight calf muscles that sometimes contribute to this injury.This night splint for plantar fasciitis and Achilles tendonitis fits either foot as well as either sex. And while the orthotic is designed for use at night, it features a slip-resistant sole for trips out of bed.The night splint for plantar fascia stretch is lightweight and the design is relatively open on the front, making it comfortable to wear while sleeping. The support is secured to the foot at three locations via simple Velcro straps.The night splint also features a soft liner for added comfort.Achilles Tendonitis and Plantar Fasciitis Night SplintPlantar fasciitis refers to painful inflammation of the thick band of tissue that stretches across the bottom of one’s foot, connecting the heel to the toes and forming the arch of the foot. Achilles tendinitis is similar in that it, too, refers to painful inflammation of a soft tissue of the foot—in this case the Achilles tendon at the back of the ankle.Plantar fasciitis is caused by overloading or putting too much tension on this shock absorbing plantar fascia of the foot. Achilles tendonitis is caused by putting repetitive or intense strain on the tendon.

product_title: Green Hills of Africa
product_description:
His second major venture into nonfiction (after Death in the Afternoon, 1932), Green Hills of Africa is Ernest Hemingway's lyrical journal of a month on safari in the great game country of East Africa, where he and his wife, Pauline, journeyed in December of 1933. Hemingway's well-known interest in - and fascination with - big-game hunting is magnificently captured in this evocative account of his trip.

In examining the poetic grace of the chase, and the ferocity of the kill, Hemingway also looks inward, seeking to explain the lure of the hunt and the primal undercurrent that comes alive on the plains of Africa. Yet Green Hills of Africa is also an impassioned portrait of the glory of the African landscape, and of the beauty of a wilderness that was, even then, being threatened by the incursions of man.

product_title: Baby Milk Warmer, Baby Bottle Steamer, Breastmilk Warmer, Food Heater, Breastmilk Defrost, Smart Temp Controller Double Bottles Infant Formula Heater with Cleaning Brush Set, BPA Free
product_description:
NUBITE 4-in-1 Simple Serve Bottle Warmer and Pacifier Steamer

Why Choose NUBITE Baby Milk Warmer?

An infant milk heater is safer, more precise, faster, and easier to use than conventional bottle warmers.

The high temperature of these heaters can be damaging to the antibodies and nutrients contained in

breast milk. This baby bottle warmer features on warm milk, defrost, warm formula and steam, which can meet your needs to feeding your baby.

Main Function Heating Time

The heating time varies with bottle material and water volume(Please add enough water according to manual)

45°C Warm Milk → 5~7 Minutes → Temperature Adjustment from 30~90°C

55°C Defrost → 9~11 Minutes → Temperature Adjustment from 30~90°C

75°C Warm Formula → 13~16 Minutes → Temperature Adjustment from 30~90°C

100°C Steam → Steam Time Adjustment 1~30 Minutes

Don't Use Microwave.

Never warm milk or baby food by boiling or warming in a microwave‚ which heats the milk or formula

unevenly, causing hot spots. A bottle that feels tepid on the outside may be scorching at its center,

causing your baby’s mouth to burn, and destroying the nutrients in milk.

Make Sure to Test It

A baby bottle warmer is a big help, but you always need to test the final temperature for baby's milk or

food before offering. Just shake a few drops on your inner wrist is the best way - it should feel luke warm, never hot.

Make Life More Simple

NUBITE baby bottle warmer is a perfect helper for parents who have a baby, help you make the

feeding simple. It’s convenient for putting on countertop or nightstand and portable for trip, also a wonderful baby shower gift!

Please read our manual carefully before using. If you have any question, please email to us.

This milk warmer is also compact enough to fit on a nightstand and countertop, so you don't have to head all the way to the kitchen for night feedings with this baby bottle milk heater.

Further, the bottle warmer anti-dry heating system can disconnect power sources automatically and will beep as a warning when constant temperature no water in device, which makes your life more simple and convenient.

product_title: Red Flame Sword - Beginner Tropical Live Aquarium Plant
product_description: Requiring little attention while providing tons of color and texture to the home aquarium, the Red Flame is a great sword plant for beginners. Hardy and undemanding, its wide tall leaves add swaying movement and a lush backdrop to planted community tanks. Echinodorus Red Flame is a hybrid between Echinodorus schlueteri 'Leopard' and Echinodorus barthii. Red Flame is very similar in appearance to The Ozelot Sword, but with larger swatches of red running along its leaves compared to the leopard-like spots of the Ozelot. The Red Flame is a relatively easy plant to maintain, but grows rather large in the aquarium. Use this plant as a background in the smaller aquarium, and as a mid-ground focal point in the larger aquarium. Do not allow the leaves of this plant to shade neighboring plants. It requires a moderate level of light of 2 to 3 watts per gallon provided by full spectrum (5000-7000K) bulbs. Reproduction within this species is by adventitious plants, side shoots, and rhizome division. Simply allow the plant to reproduce by one of the above methods, and when the new plant forms its own leaves, separate and replant in another location of the aquarium. The Red Flame is sensitive to copper, so this type of medication should not be added to the aquarium where it is contained. Approximate Shipping Size: Bare Root 4" to 6"
product_bullet_point:
IMPORTANT! PLEASE READ BEFORE ORDERING: Please note that during times of extreme weather, live plants will suffer due to extreme temperatures. During winter, do not order live plants when temperatures are expected to go below 20F at the lowest point during the day. During summer, avoid ordering plants when temperatures are above 100F.
You get 1 young Red Flame Sword. An easy live aquarium plant specie for any freshwater aquarium. PLEASE NOTE THE RED LEAVES WILL START COMING OUT ONCE ACCLIMATED TO YOUR AQUARIUM. Todo el mundo está buscando algo un poco diferente en estos días, ya sea para regalar un cumpleaños, día de San Valentín, Navidad o simplemente una forma de decir gracias. Creemos que tenemos algo diferente aquí para ti, increíblemente simple pero eficaz como una luz nocturna, luz de humor o como una decoración en tu casa u oficina.

1. Efecto de visión 3D: especialmente en la oscuridad o tomar una fotografía, ¡la emoción de la visión será fuerte!

product_description: SR405EQM Quilted Maple 5-String Electric Bass Guitar Dragon Eye Burst. For 25 years the SR has given bass players a modern alternative. Embraced by bassists over the decades, the iconic series continues to excite with its smooth, fast neck, lightweight body and perfectly matched electronics. The SR405EQM is a handsome 5-string bass designed for the experienced player. The bass starts with an immaculately finished Mahogany body topped with gorgeous quilted maple. product_title: With or Without You: A wonderfully emotional story of one love over two lifetimes...
product_description:
Have you ever made a life-changing decision before wondering if you made the right one...?

When Liv and Nate walked up the aisle, Liv knew she was marrying the one, her soul mate and her best friend.
Six years later, it feels like routine and friendship is all they have left in common. What happened to the fun, the excitement, the lust, the love?

In the closing moments of 1999, Liv and Nate decide to go their separate ways, but at the last minute, Liv wavers. Should she stay or should she go?

Over the next twenty years we follow the parallel stories to discover if Liv's life, heart and future have been better with Nate... Or without him?

Perfect for the fans of Jojo Moyes, Lucy Diamond and Marian Keyes.

Praise for With or Without You:

'Cold Feet meets Sliding Doors. This is one of the best books I've EVER read' Mandy Baggot, author of One Last Greek Summer.

'This is the first Shari Low book I have read, but definitely won't be the last. A keeper - to reread again!' Zara Stonely, bestselling author of The Wedding Date.

'This was a very entertaining book throughout and one I really enjoyed reading, even the parts that had me in floods of tears' That Thing She Reads.

'I will certainly be recommending this book to everyone who will listen to me! Stunning!' Stardust Book Reviews.

'This book made me cry and laugh in equal measure' Leanne Wilkins, NetGalley.

'A light, easy read romance' Moirelyn Jewula, NetGalley.

It straightens! It curls! It smoothes! It shines! Drybar's The Tress Press Straightening Iron, 1" is a dual-purpose iron that allows you to quickly style even the thickest hair into super-sleek straight looks or add a bit of wave or curl.
Ionic technology uses the power of negative ions to reduce frizz for smoother, shinier tresses. Infrared Technology heats hair from the inside out to help maintain healthy locks. 1" (2.54 cm) floating plates provide constant contact with the hair to straighten in a single pass.
Rounded edges allow you to easily wrap hair around the barrel for waves and curls. Heats up to 450°F. Features a 60-minute automatic safety shut-off and professional length 9 ft (2.74 m) cord. Universal voltage for overseas travel without a converter. Guaranteed with a 2-year limited warranty.
HOW TO USE: Work in 1‒2” (2.5-5 cm) cleanly parted, brushed sections. TO STRAIGHTEN: Hold iron horizontally. Clamp hair at the root and slowly pull through to the ends, slightly beveling toward the face to prevent static. TO CURL: Hold iron vertically. Clamp hair midway through the section, then twist the iron away from your face 180 degrees and pull forward through to the ends. The slower you pull, the greater the curl. For waves, pull through more quickly.
Created for the perfect blowout. Our philosophy is simple: Focus on one thing and be the best at it. For us that's blowouts! We created a full line of hair products and tools to achieve and maintain the perfect blowout.

product_title: Jade Leaf Organic Matcha Green Tea Powder - Authentic Japanese Origin - Premium Second Harvest Culinary Grade (1.06 Ounce)
product_description: FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS What grade of Matcha is this, and how do I use it? This is Culinary Grade Matcha, which is an affordable way to add a delicious, healthy boost to smoothies, lattes, baked goods, and other dishes. What's the difference between Culinary and Ceremonial grades? Simple: Culinary grade is meant for mixing into recipes as an ingredient, while Ceremonial grade is meant to be prepared traditionally as a tea (just mixed with hot water and whisked). Culinary grade is more affordable for day to day use, making it easy to fit the health benefits of Matcha into your diet. Does it contain caffeine? Yes, each half-teaspoon (1g) serving contains roughly 34mg of caffeine, about 1/3 a cup of coffee. However, Matcha also contains L-Theanine, which has a calming and leveling affect, so it doesn't make you feel jittery or wired like coffee does. Are there other use cases for Culinary Matcha? Yes! Many of our customers make a healthy facial mask using our Culinary Grade, by mixing it with just a bit of water to form a paste. Where does this Matcha come from? Our Matcha is grown by organically family farms near the city of Uji in Kyoto, Japan. What if I don't like it? If you are not 100% satisfied with your purchase for any reason, just email us and we'll refund your order in full, no questions asked.

product_title: Measy FHD686 Extensor HDMI inalámbrico, transmisor y receptor wifi 2.4G / 5.8G compatible con Full HD con salida de bucle, 500 ft para proyector, monitor, iglesia, oficina, hogar
product_description:
El extensor HDMI inalámbrico Measy FHD686 transmite audio y video Full HD desde cualquier fuente de dispositivo al televisor de forma inalámbrica. No se requiere ninguna conexión de cable entre el dispositivo fuente y el televisor. Puede ver la televisión Full HD libremente desde cualquier lugar. Es fácil de instalar, enchufar y usar, no es necesario instalar ningún software, no es necesario realizar ninguna configuración. ¡Se puede instalar en 2 minutos! Utiliza la última tecnología inalámbrica distribuida y la señal puede ser clara y fluida a través de una única pared o techo que no sea de alta densidad, sin interferencias de imagen y sonido. El extensor HDMI inalámbrico garantiza un flujo de señal fluido desde cualquier dispositivo AV con salida HDMI a un televisor. Proporciona una experiencia de transmisión de medios inmersiva gracias a la transmisión Full HD estable y sin comprimir.

Especificación
Estándares HDMI: HDMI 1.4, HDCP1.4
Resolución HDMI: hasta 1080p a 60Hz
Distancia de transmisión: hasta 656 pies / 200 m (en el espacio abierto)
Formato de audio: sonido de alta calidad de 1080p
Interfaz de entrada / salida: Interfaz HDMI
Velocidad máxima de transmisión de datos: 6.75Gbps
Estándares de transmisión inalámbrica: IEEE802.11 a / b / g / n
Frecuencia de funcionamiento 2.4g (150Mbps), 5.8G (300Mbps)
Tasa de frecuencia Ir: 38KHz
Material de la carcasa: Plástico transparente < br> Entrada de energía: 5V / 2A
Tamaño de la máquina: 128 * 930 * 26 mm
Temperatura de funcionamiento: -5 ℃ ~ 70 ℃
Temperatura de almacenamiento: -4 ~ 140 ℉ / 20 ~ 60 ℃

Paquete:
adaptador de corriente * 2
manual de usuario * 1,
cable de infrarrojos * 1
product_bullet_point:
【Admite uno o más receptores. Utilice equipos y escenarios de aplicación】 El extensor HDMI inalámbrico FHD686 puede admitir 1 transmisor hasta 4 receptores. Necesita comprar más receptor adicionalmente si es necesario. Asegúrese de que el transmisor y el receptor funcionen en el mismo canal cuando utilice más receptores. A menudo, el canal 5 y el canal 9 funcionan mejor y con menos interferencia que otros canales.
【Puede atravesar la pared, hasta 150 m 500 pies (línea de visión)】FHD686 puede transmitir 5-30 m / 32 pies-100 pies cuando atraviesa una pared como una pared de vidrio, una pared de madera o una pared hueca, pero no puede pasar a través o solo hasta aproximadamente 3-5 m cuando pasa a través de una pared delgada de concreto. La distancia variará según el entorno. La pared, los ladrillos o el vidrio acortarán el rango de cobertura de la señal o causarán una pérdida significativa de
【Baja latencia, con bucle de salida local.】 Es bueno compartir PC o reproductores en una pantalla grande. Pero el tiempo de latencia es de aproximadamente 150 ms, por lo que no se recomienda para aplicaciones en tiempo real, como juegos de PC, deportes de alta velocidad. Pero el bucle de salida tiene una latencia cero y se puede usar bien para una pantalla local. Asegúrese de que los cables HDMI no sean más largos de 1,5 m, mejor menos de 1 m para evitar una gran pérdida de señal.
【Control remoto por infrarrojos, Plug and Play y sin necesidad de WIFI. 】Admite la función de extensión remota por infrarrojos de 20-60 KHZ. Puede controlar el dispositivo fuente en el receptor. Cuando se utiliza el cable de infrarrojos externo. Trate de mantener el transmisor alejado del "decodificador" y evite enviar señales infrarrojas al mismo tiempo para causar conflictos de control remoto.Verdadero Plug and Play,sin necesidad de wifi, TX y RX con incorporado señal wifi e ir.
【Utilice equipos y escenarios de aplicación】 El transmisor inalámbrico HDMI se puede conectar a cualquier dispositivo HDMI, ideal para salas de conferencias y teatros en casa. Se puede compartir fácilmente entre computadoras portátiles y televisores de alta definición, como cajas de cable / satélite, cámaras de seguridad domésticas, DVD, DVR, decodificadores, IPTV, CCTV, laptops, PC y reproductores de Blu-ray, etc. La compatibilidad es muy buena.

product_title: Luz Solar Exterior, Focos LED Exterior Solares con Sensor de Movimiento Lampara Solar Exterior 120° lluminación IP65 Impermeable Potentes Lampara Solar Exterior para Jardin Garaje Terraza
product_description:
¿Se siente inseguro en el camino oscuro pero siente que no tiene que detener la luz?

¿Le preocupa que alguien pueda entrar y salir en su jardín, frente a la puerta o en la puerta del garaje, pero no puede saberlo?

¿Cansado de tropezar y tropezar en la oscuridad?

Es hora de comprar una luz de seguridad con sensor solar para mantener las luces encendidas y ahorrar energía.


¿Alguna vez ha comprado algunas luces de emergencia pero el brillo de la iluminación y el tiempo de iluminación no son satisfactorios?

Debido al diseño integrado de la luz de seguridad tradicional, es posible que no pueda almacenar energía por completo debido al escaso ángulo de luz en la ubicación.

Nuestro diseño independiente resuelve este problema a la perfección. Además, utilizamos paneles solares con un área más grande y una mayor eficiencia de conversión para garantizar una mayor vida útil de la iluminación.


Fuente de luz COB de alta potencia

La fuente de luz COB tiene menos caída de luz, emisión de luz uniforme, sin manchas y un rendimiento de reproducción de color fuerte. Alta eficiencia de disipación de calor y larga vida útil.


Especificaciones:

Material: plástico ABS

Tamaño del producto: 14,8 * 12,7 * 2,4 cm

Tamaño del panel solar: 12,8 * 13,1 * 1,5 cm

Batería: batería de litio de 3,7 V 1200 mAh

Consumo de energía: 1,5 W

Brillo: 180LM
product_bullet_point:
Práctico diseño dividido: Con la ayuda del diseño separado del colector solar y los paneles de luz, el colector se puede instalar en posiciones con buena intensidad de luz y la lámpara en posiciones con altos requisitos de luz durante mucho tiempo. Además, el colector solar de alta calidad aumenta la eficiencia del almacenamiento de energía en un 10%, lo que mejora perfectamente la resistencia a la luz.
3 modos de inducción para elegir: con el sensor sensible que ofrece detección de gran angular de 120 °, la luz exterior puede proporcionar una buena iluminación de inducción. Se incorporan tres modos de iluminación humanizados: a. Apague el modo de brillo total inductivo b. Modo de brillo completo inductivo medio brillante; C. Siempre en modo de luz completa. Puedes elegir según tus necesidades reales.
Fuente de luz COB de alta calidad: la luz solar utiliza una fuente de luz COB, ofrece un 10% más de brillo y menos pérdida de luz. La lámpara solar emite una luz más uniforme, sin puntos de luz y con un fuerte rendimiento de reproducción cromática. Y la alta eficiencia de disipación de calor contribuye a una larga vida útil, definitivamente una buena opción para usted.
Resistente al agua y al polvo: la luz solar cumple con el estándar IP65 y garantiza una protección calificada a prueba de agua y polvo. Incluso con lluvia y viento, el producto no se daña fácilmente. Adecuado para patios, puertas de garaje, jardines, puertas de entrada y otras escenas.
Fácil montaje: no se requiere cableado adicional. Solo necesita taladrar los tornillos adjuntos en la pared para completar el accesorio. Recomendamos encarecidamente instalar los paneles solares en un lugar con suficiente luz del día para maximizar la iluminación nocturna a largo plazo. La altura de instalación ideal es de aproximadamente 1,8 ma 2,5 m.

product_title: The Love Calendar for Couples – A Romantic Month with Your Partner
product_description: The Love Calendar for Couples is the perfect romantic gift, especially for newlyweds and couples looking to bring a new spark to their relationship.
product_bullet_point:
Do you wish your relationship was more romantic? Or perhaps you simply need some inspiration for fun activities to enjoy with your partner? Then the Love Calendar for Couples is exactly what you need.
Just like an advent calendar, this calendar contains numbered windows to open on the day that corresponds to the number. However, unlike an advent calendar, this calendar contains 31 windows, and you can start at any day you want and use it at any time of the year.
And best of all, instead of getting a piece of chocolate when you open a window you get to select between three different activities to enjoy with your partner.
The activities can be either fun, romantic, or adventurous, and in order to fit your schedule there is always a choice between doing something quick and easy and something a bit more advanced.
Please note that the calendar can be used at any time of the year, and it's made for two grown-ups of any gender that are in a romantic relationship. The size of the calendar is 16.5″ x 11.7″ (42 x 29.7 cm) when unfolded, and 8.25″ x 11.7″ (21 x 29.7 cm) folded.

product_description: ■ヒューゴボス(ドイツ語:Hugo Boss フーゴボス[*])はドイツの高級ファッション商標であり、ドイツで設立された男性ファッション中心のファッション商標である。 最初は軍服のデザインなどをしていたが、2次世界大戦後、ヒューゴ・ボスの死後、スーツを発表して紳士服ブランドとして定着する。 スーツのような背広だけでなく、女性、メガネ、サングラス、香水、靴など幅広く展開する。 現在は世界100ヵ国余りに進出した。 ■洗練され、完全に現代的なHUGOは、ヒューゴー·ボスの仕立て方を重視し、若々しいエネルギーでそれを遮り、鋭いカットと清潔なデザインの衣服をカジュアルなエッジで表現している。 新しい最高ブランド責任者のインゴ·ウィルツ氏の指導の下、HUGOのメンズウェアは、仕事日から週末までの狭くなるスペースに巧みに対処し、流動的で、その瞬間に自信を持つ、古典的な既製服のホッチキス針を再アニメーション化しています。 ハイブリッドで高層作物、スリムフィット、テーパードのデニムとラウンジのズボン、きつくカットされたクルーネックのTシャツ、そして箱のようなタートルネックのプルオーバーは、現代的な仕立て方と90年代のシルエットとのよく調和がとれていることを物語っている。 ブランド遺産と現代的最新情報とのスマートな相互作用は、アウターウェアにも反映されており、ストームフラップのアクセントのあるトレンチコート、完璧なミニマム爆撃機ジャケット、そしてスマートなウールコートは、現代人にとっては慎重に再考されています。 厳選されたピースは、パンキーな落書きされたデザインとラインの更新されたロゴを使い、ブランドのデザイン言語をさらにリフレッシュします。 ハウスに関連した強い単色の色調でレンダリングされたHUGOのコレクションは、強い形を削り、フォロワーを率いて主導権を握ることを拒否した。
product_bullet_point:

product_title: Ulincos Auto Relay U1914 with 14AWG Wire Harness, 12V DC 30/40A SPDT 5-Pin (Pack of 2)
product_description:
About the Relay
Relay is an electrical control device that usually used in automatic control circuit.
The relay in fact is an automatic switch which uses a smaller current to control a larger current.

What's the Relay Used for
Compatible with almost all automobiles and devices equipped with a 12V DC power supply.
Like starter kills, power door lock/actuator control, change a low current output to high current, add ignition/accessory outputs,
control motors/other electronics. It is also suitable for automobile used for control, alarms, horn, headlight and more.

About the Relay Pins
Pins 85 & 86 - are used to turn 'on' the relay. You need a positive (+) and negative (-) power source to turn on the relay.
- Pin 85 - is usually negative (-)
- Pin 86 - is usually positive (+)
Pin 30 - is either a (+) or (-) source that feeds Pin 87 or Pin 87a
Pin 87 - when the relay is 'on': Pin 30 and Pin 87 are connected
Pin 87a - when the relay is 'off': Pin 30 and Pin 87a are connected

About the Wire harness
Five 14AWG wires, rated for 20A:
#Black (85) – to Ground
#White (86) – to Switch or Trigger
#Blue (30)- to Battery Positive
#Red (87a)- Normally Closed Contact
#Yellow (87) - Normally Open Contact

What's Note
* The relay is rated for 30A, while the socket 14AWG wires are not big enough for the rated 30/40 amps.
If you are intending to run 30 amps continuously, you could remove the spade contacts from the connector, carefully open the crimps
securing the wire to the contact and recrimp/solder 10 gauge wires to it. Also, you can use 6.3 mm female connectors
to connect directly to the relay pins. The relay should be good for 30 amps.

About the Package
2 X Relay
product_bullet_point:
SPDT Relay - Single Pole Double Throw, you can use them to open or close a circuit -- or go from bright to dim on your headlights
30/40A Relay – It is rated to handle 40 amps of load at 12V DC in the Normally Open position (PIN 87), and 30 amps of load at 12V DC in the Normally Closed position (PIN 87a). You can use it in any circuit less than 30A
With the Wire Harness - Makes relay installation a breeze. If one goes bad, just unplug it from the socket and plug in a new one
Each socket has a male and female slide. You can connect as many of these together next to each other as possible. This makes mounting them easy and clean looking
Wide range of use, can be used in automotive setup, seat warming, vehicle lighting system, car sound system and various other applications

product_title: The Time in Between (The Magdalene Series Book 3)
product_description:
After a painful loss, Cady Moreland is coming to Magdalene to start the next chapter of her life. A chapter that began eighteen years ago but had a heartbreaking ending. The time in between was full of family and friendship, but Cady could never get the man she fell in love with all those years ago out of her heart.

Coert Yeager has learned to live without the girl who entered his life right when she shouldn’t and exited delivering a crippling blow he never would have suspected. The time in between was full of failing to find what he was missing…and life-altering betrayal.

But when that girl shows up in Magdalene and buys the town’s beloved lighthouse, even if Coert wants to avoid her, he can’t. A fire in town sparks a different kind of flame that won’t be ignored.

As Cady and Coert question the actions of the two young adults they once were thrown into earth-shattering circumstances, can they learn from what came in between and find each other again?

That is why Maymom develops more than 12 sizes of flanges spanning from 13 mm up to 36 mm to fit the average mothers and those mothers who need special sizes (e.g. 13, 15, 17, 36 mm). There are improvements of Maymom flange over the original spectra design -
1. In addition to Spectra's duckbills, you can use Maymom duckbills or Maymom valve/membrane system with Maymom flange.
2. In addition to fitting Spectra's backflow protector, you can use Maymom long stem, as well as short stem backflow protectors. You can also use Maymom tubing connector (sold separately e.g. ASIN B0033B9CZ2) to connect Maymom flange to many other popular breastpumps on the market.

Wide Mouth Flange x2

product_title: Jericho
Mamá en busca del polvo perdido (Harpercollins Nf)
product_description:
Hay gente muy motivada con ganas de hacer grandes gestas, como subir un ocho mil o sacarse una carrera universitaria pasados los cuarenta. Paz no.

Paz tiene tres hijos, un marido estándar, un jefe gilipollas y lo más parecido a tener tiempo para ella es conseguir ir sola a comprar al Carrefour. Pero sí que tiene una misión: se ha propuesto echar un polvo, no, UN POLVAZO, con el padre de sus hijos. Con preliminares y todo.

Solo tiene que conseguir un momento, de más de dos minutos si no es mucho pedir, en el que los dos tengan ganas, duchados si puede ser, que no estén muy cansados, preferiblemente depilados, que no estén casualmente enfadados y, por supuesto, que los niños se duerman pronto.

No puede ser tan difícil, ¿verdad? ¿VERDAD?

¿QUE CUÁNDO EMPEZÓ TODO? Podría decir que la hecatombe se desató un día que sucedió algo especial, una singularidad cósmica: los niños se durmieron pronto. Y Didier y yo teníamos ganas de mambo, así que nos pusimos al lío, aunque, ¡oh, destino!, los niños estaban ocupando todas las superficies blandas de la casa.

Sin embargo, estábamos fogosos, de modo que nos fuimos al suelo. Y descubrí una verdad horripilante: que el amor es joven, pero mis rodillas se ve que no.

¡¡¡UN DERRAME!!!

Un puto derrame se me hizo en la rodilla izquierda, que se me puso MORADA como una berenjena vasca. ¡¡Si solo tengo treinta y nueve años!! ¡¿En qué momento de mi vida me he convertido en una SEÑORA a quien le sale UN DERRAME POR ECHAR UN POLVO?!

Esto no se acaba aquí. Llamadme loca, pero TENGO UNA MISIÓN: Voy a echar un SEÑOR POLVAZO con el padre de mis hijos.

product_title: El amor de un padre
product_description:
El amor es sinónimo de dolor...

A veces, el amor nos rompe por dentro, convirtiendo nuestro corazón en piezas de un puzle que somos incapaces de volver a encajar hasta que aquella que faltaba, que parecía perdida, se presenta, entra en tu vida y, sin saber cómo, vuelves a estar completo.
Me llamo Daniel y aprendí lo que se siente cuando te estrujan el corazón y a la misma vez la felicidad gracias a Náyade, mi hija y mundo. Es por ello que el tiempo fue el único testigo de mis cicatrices, y cuando creí que volvería a caer, el amor me sostuvo para enseñarme, una vez más, a ser fuerte.
Mi historia es parte de la vida, y la vida no es un camino de rosas. También, para mí, fue un desorden de sucesos que a punto estuvo de destruirme, pues el infierno quiso quitarme lo que significa el amor de un padre.

This comprehensive volume discusses in vitro laboratory development of insulin-producing cells. It encompasses multiple aspects of islet biology—from embryonic development and stem cell differentiation to clinical studies in islet transplantation, regulation of islet beta-cell regeneration, pancreatic progenitors, mathematical modelling of islet development, epigenetic regulation, and much more. The chapter authors represent leading laboratories from around the world who contribute their international perspectives and global expertise. Collectively, they provide the reader with a concise yet detailed knowledge of processes and current developments in islet regenerative biology.



Pancreatic Islet Biology, part of the Stem Cell Biology and Regenerative Medicine series, is essential reading for researchers and clinicians in stem cells or endocrinology, especially those focusing on diabetes.

Just the right size
Spot clean with cold water, tumble dry on low

Note: Please give 48-72 hours to the pillow to fully expand. You can also tab or press the pillow a few times to hasten expansion.

If your pillows still do not expand, please use the following methods to spring them up:

1. Put the Pillows in the Dryer with 2 Tennis Balls:
Start off by placing your pillow in the dryer with 2 tennis balls (preferably wrapped in a cloth or socks separately). The tennis ball will hit the pillow, fluffing up the filling. Tumble dry low for an hour to make sure your pillow become fluffier and softer.

2. Leave the Pillow in the Sun:
By placing the pillows in the sun for a few hours on a bright day will evaporate the moisture that builds up overnight from its use and the pillows will fluff up over the course of the day. You could also hang the pillows outside on a clothes line.

product_title: Christmas in Silver Bell Falls
product_description: Her attitude is less than merry and bright…Melanie Harper and Christmas do not see eye to eye. While most people celebrate and look forward to the holidays, it's something she has come to dread. When she receives a gift from an unlikely source - a house in the quaint town of Silver Bell Falls - her immediate reaction is to reject it. After all, with a name like that, you're pretty much guaranteed to be surrounded by people who love Christmas!He sees it as the most wonderful time of the year…Josiah Stone is all about peace on earth and goodwill toward man. Maybe it's because he's the sheriff of a town named after a beloved Christmas song, but that doesn't make it any less true. Christmas is his favorite time of year and living in Silver Bell Falls where everyone feels the same and celebrates it nearly year-round only adds to his festive outlook on life. Can a white Christmas change everything?When Melanie is forced to stay in Silver Bell Falls during the actual holiday season, she's less than thrilled. But after meeting the sexy sheriff she finds that there is something to be said about the magic of Christmas.

product_description: 《지적 대화를 위한 넓고 얕은 지식》 제로 편이 고대 이전의 지식, 모든 지식 이전에 알아야 하는 지식을 다룬다면, 1권과 2권은 고대 이후부터 현대까지 우리에게 좀 더 가까운 시간의 지식들을 다룬다. 고대 이후는 이원론이 지배하는 시대였기에, 책의 구조는 이분법을 따른다. 현실 세계를 지배자와 피지배자로 구분해 어렵고 복잡한 지식들을 하나의 단순한 구조로 재편한다. 독자들은 기존에 없었던 채사장 작가의 전체를 꿰뚫는 방식에 열광했다. 방대한 분량의 역사부터 마르크스, 자본주의, 신자유주의, 보수와 진보, 다양한 정치 사회 문제 등 반드시 알아야만 대화가 가능한 기초 지식들, 그러나 단편적으로만 접해서 연결되지 않았던 세부 지식들이 하나의 큰 틀 안에서 정리되는 지적 체험은 오직 「지대넓얕」으로만 가능했다. 어렵고 딱딱하던 인문학 분야 판도를 뒤바꾼 책. 출간 즉시 베스트셀러에 오르는 것을 시작으로, 200만 부 누적 판매를 돌파해 더블 밀리언셀러를 기록하며, 장장 5년간 스테디셀러의 자리에서 꿈쩍도 하지 않은 책. 발음하기도 낯설고 어려운 '지대넓얕'이라는 말을 유행시키고, 유사 콘셉트의 TV 프로그램까지 탄생시킨 책, 기초 상식에 목말라 있던 보통 사람들이 거리낌 없이 토론하게 하고 뉴스를 주체적으로 보게 하고 선거에서 주관을 갖게 한 책, 80대 독자가 독학을 시작하고 중학생 독자가 인문학을 읽게 하고 직장인들이 독서 모임을 갖게 하는 등 세대 불문 남녀노소 읽을 수 있도록 쉽고 재미있게 쓰였다고 평가받는 책이다.
product_bullet_point:
韓国より配送。 営業日基準で7日から17日かかります。
“이 책은 당신 삶의 가장 앞에 위치해야 한다. 이 책은 모든 지식의 목차에 해당한다.” - 지식을 알고 싶으면 선(先)지식이 필요하다! 지금까지 그리고 앞으로도 끊임없이 얻어야 하는 모든 지식을 위해, 당신의 가장 밑바탕에 마련해야 하는 지식.
'제로' 편에 이어, 출간 5년 만에 처음으로 개정증보판이 나왔다. 거칠고 부족했던 부분은 부드럽게 매만지고 채워 넣었다. 낡은 이야기는 시대에 맞게 바꿨다. 작가 채사장이 출간 후 많은 독자와 만나 나누었던 이야기들은 책을 개정하는 데 도움이 되었다. 꼼꼼하게 수선된 개정판을 읽는 순간, 왜 지난 5년간 이 책의 아성이 깨지지 않았는지 확인하게 될 것이다.
《지적 대화를 위한 넓고 얕은 지식》 2 [현실 너머] 편 : 철학 / 과학 / 예술 / 종교 / 신비 - 어떤 문제든 대화할 수 있게 돕는, 가장 쉬운 인문학 입문서. 교양인으로서 꼭 알아두어야 하는 기본 지식이 하나의 구조로 연결됨으로써 방대했던 지식의 구조가 쉽고 입체적으로 연결된다!

1. Antes de lavar, peine las extensiones de abajo hacia arriba. No mucho.

3. Segundo lavado con acondicionador. Siempre peina suavemente y lava con agua fría.
4. Seque las extensiones con una toalla y déjelas secar naturalmente. No exponer al sol.

product_description:
Get the 8-inch Uno Casa Cast Iron Tortilla Press and add some freshness to dinner tonight.

The cast iron in the Uno Casa Tortilla Press not only makes for a sturdy, quality product, it also makes it easier to actually press the tortillas! The heavy top means you don’t need to strain to make a perfectly round circle of dough because the force of gravity does this for you.

Already pre-seasoned, you can use the tortilla press right out of the box. As it works best with a piece of parchment paper between the cast iron and the dough, we’ve included 100 pieces of parchment paper to get you started.

And there’s no more waste of money or food! When you make your own dough and cook it up in batches as you go, you always have just the right amount of food that you need. Store-bought tortillas are packed full of preservatives and additives to keep them fresher for longer, but your homemade recipes won’t have anything in them that you don’t want. The fact that homemade tastes better too is just icing on the cake.

Pro tip: Corn-based flour will yield the best results when cooking with our cast iron tortilla press. You can use all-purpose flour too, but the high gluten content makes it more elastic so the tortilla shrinks a little after pressing. To avoid any shrinkage, just let your all-purpose flour dough rest a little longer!

Versatile and multipurpose, this taco maker is for more than just great tortillas. It’s also a roti maker, flatbread press, chapati maker, pie shell maker and more. So it’s perfect not just for Mexican night, but for Indian night and dessert night too. The sky’s the limit.

product_title: Baby Inheritance (Inherit Love Book 1) (English Edition)
product_description:
It only took a day for her to lose everything.

But give her nine months and a pact with her best friend’s brother, and she can get it all back.

Valentina

It sucks waking up rich, then finding out your father has stolen everything you had. But a clause in my grandmother’s will can solve all my problems.

There’s one catch – I need to have a baby.

I’ve always wanted to be a mother. To have a family.

But I’ll need to beat my rival cousin to the delivery room in order to inherit.

Good thing my best friend’s devilishly handsome brother needs a cash injection to keep his construction company afloat.

I’ve had a secret crush on him since before I needed a bra, so making a baby with him sounds like a dream come true.

Now I’ve just got to convince him to get me pregnant.

And pray he doesn’t break my heart in the process.

Hudson

Growing up, I never paid much attention to my kid sister’s friend Valentina.

But damn has she changed. Now she’s all curves and legs that go on forever.

One minute I’m floundering to make payroll, the next she’s telling me that she needs someone to get her pregnant.

If it all goes according to plan, she’ll split fifty million dollars with me.

My brain hurts from the possible complications, but the way she bites her bottom lip when she asks—it makes the wrong head do the thinking.

Solving my financial problems in exchange for stud service…

How soon can I start?

product_title: My Very Own Exchanji: An Interactive Gender Transformation Romance
product_description:
What would you do if you found a magical board game that magically transformed you in some VERY surprising ways? Would you dare to keep playing? Could you uncover its mysteries? And how would the rest of your life turn out?

In My Very Own Exchanji, YOU get to make all of these choices and more as you return to the world of Alyson Belle's classic book Exchanji, joining four young friends on the magical and hilarious romantic transformation adventure of a lifetime and seeing all the different ways their fateful night might have turned out. You play the book as Connor, one of the men, and when you find a dusty old board game called Exchanji (An Exciting Game of Changes for Consenting Adults) in a closet, things start to get wild as soon as the dice start rolling! Swapped bodies and surprising transformations are only the start of this crazy night...

Not only can you pick which romantic encounters happen to Connor throughout the book, but you also get to choose from dozens and dozens of branching paths as the night gets crazier and crazier: Will you go along with the board game's magic or fight it every step of the way? Will you wind up with your girlfriend Maya, the hotheaded Kelsey, or even your best friend Frank? Do you dare to step beyond the portal and enter the magical realms of Exchanjia? With over 400 pages of possibilities and sixteen completely unique endings, the choices you make on this fateful day will affect Connor and every one of his friends for the rest of their lives (or maybe beyond)!

Can you make the right choices to have fun, stay alive, and uncover all of the mysteries of the world of Exchanji? There's only one way to find out!

Unlike traditional books, this is a branching narrative story that can be read multiple times with different events throughout. At the end of each section there are several hyperlinks indicating choices you can make for Connor, just like a game. You can tap your e-reader/tablet or click the link in your browser (depending on where you’re reading this) to make the selection you want, and you’ll be transported to that section to continue the story. While it’s possible to use your back buttons to go back a step, you’ll probably have the most fun if you treat the decisions as permanent until your next read-through, just like Connor and his friends would have to do!

product_title: HAOHUNT Automatic Soap Dispenser Infrared Liquid Hand Soap Dispenser touchless with 17oz Large Capacity Applicable for Kitchen Bathroom School Hotel Hospital Restaurant
product_description:
Product details:

Package Included:

1* Sanitizer Dispenser(No batteries included)
1* User Instruction Manual

Use Instructions:

1. Install the battery correctly according to the instructions. (4 AA batteries required and need to be purchased separately)
2. Add the disinfectant according to the instructions.
3. Tap the power button, the indicator will be on.
4. Move your palm towards the IR detection area of the sprayer, the distance between your palm and the detection area should be kept within 1-2cm. Then the device will spray disinfectant.

How to Assemble the batteries

1: Fix the bottle body to rotate 90º counterclockwise.
2: Lifting the fuselage.
3: Open the battery cover by turning it counterclockwise.
4: Install the battery correctly according to the positive and negative poles(+/-) marked on the battery compartment.
5: Align the unlocking mark on the battery cover with the arrow mark on the sidewall of the fuselage.
6: Rotate the battery cover clockwise with only the lock mark aligned with the arrow mark on the sidewall of the fuselage.
7: Point the disinfectant bottle into the bottom slot of the fuselage and gently rotate it counterclockwise until it is firm.

Warm Tips:

1. Don't put the product into water or wash the device with water, to avoid electrical shock. You can use paper or wet cloth to clean it.
2. Do not block the nozzle with hands or foreign matters, and do not lay down the device body, so as to avoid damage caused by liquid pouring into the machine body.
3. If you don't use this product for a long time, please use clear water to pump and wash it many times, so as to avoid blockage.
4. When the product runs out of power or will be not used for a long time, please take out the battery.
product_bullet_point:
Automatic Soap Dispenser：This touchless Sanitizer dispenser was designed with the built-in infrared sensor, it can detect your hand instantly when you put your hands before the sensor and it would spray the sanitizer automatically. No-touch design to avoid cross-infection.
Quick Respond & Waterproof：High-quality sensor, 0.25s quick response. One body waterproof design, no need to worry about splitting water to get inside the motor. With an inner anti-leakage silicone pad to prevent the liquid from corroding batteries.
Hangable design：This Automatic Sanitizer Dispenser can be hanged on a hook. With this feature, you can hang on a wall, space-saving and you don't need to worry about knocking it over.
Simple Design & Large Capacity：This soap dispenser adopts a touch button, 1 button design simple to use. 17oz large capacity bottle to accommodate more sanitizer. (Need to assemble 4*AA batteries before using it and batteries need to be purchased separately).
Multiple Applicable：It can compatible with most kinds of liquid soap, such as hand sanitizer, shower gel, shampoo, and so on (Notice: It is not a foaming dispenser and does not spray foam). It can be placed in the kitchen, bathroom, or public places.

Universal Compatibility
